<!DOCTYPE subsection SYSTEM "mingle_help.dtd">
<section title="Manage existing project team members" id="manage_existing_team_members">
  <subsection title="Change user role" collapsed = 'true'>
    <p>From the team list, you can locate the user you want to update and select the <cref topic="user_roles">role</cref> your want him to have on your project.</p>
    <screenshot alttext="Change role" src="resources/images/team_page_change_role.png"/>
  </subsection>
  <subsection title="Remove team member" collapsed = 'true' id="remove_team_members">
    <p>To remove existing team member, select the user you want to remove and click Remove button.</p>
    <screenshot alttext="Remove team member" src="resources/images/team_page_remove_member.png"/>
    <note>Select <link>All</link> to select all team members on the page. Select <link>None</link> to deselect all team members on the page.</note>
  </subsection>
</section>